          <text>
                    <body>
                              <p rend="align(right)">
                                        <placeName>Wilkes Barre</placeName>
                                        <date>Sept 26/52</date>
                              </p>
                              <p><addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee>!</p>
                              <p rend="indent(3)">Dr. Sir!</p>
                              <p rend="indent(4)">Your <sic>respectfull</sic>,<lb/> communication is
                                        at hand, as also the <add>Hebrew</add> for<lb/> which
                                        kindness please accept the thanks of the<lb/> whole
                                        congregation. I have been in your city<lb/> at different
                                        times, and never could find you at home<lb/> sometimes you
                                        are at <placeName>N: Orleans</placeName>, and again at
                                                  <placeName>Buff.<lb/> N. Y.</placeName> I have not
                                        neglect my promise in <sic>trieing</sic><lb/> to obtain
                                        subscribers for you, but times will not<lb/> afford at
                                        present in our place, however I think<lb/> I will be able to
                                        do so <add>?</add> shortly in getting<lb/> a few subsc:
                                        &amp; orders for some Books, I have
                                        <sic>collectit</sic><lb/> $9. for you $6 off <add>?</add>
                                        &amp; $3. from <persName>Ansbacher</persName>, also<lb/>
                                        sold two of your Prayer Books, but have not collect<lb/> the
                                        payment for them, I will do my best and<lb/> shall devote a
                                        portion of my time to the advancements<lb/> of your
                                        interest, and welfare.</p>
                              <p>My Brother will visit your city shortly, and by him<lb/> I will
                                        send all the money, also the payment for<lb/>
                                        <add>?</add>. The copy of your Law, and your Sermon
                                        which<lb/> you delivered here, it is all in my hands, and
                                        safely<lb/> taken care of it</p>
                              <p rend="indent(9)">Respectfully &amp; Obt</p>
                              <p rend="indent(9)">
                                        <persName role="author">M. W. Strause</persName>
                              </p>
                    </body>
